{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":485,"text":"I'm a designer and an educator."},{"time":3381,"text":"I'm a multitasking person, and I push my students"},{"time":6277,"text":"to fly through a very creative, multitasking design process."},{"time":12388,"text":"But how efficient is, really, this multitasking?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":17353,"text":"Let's consider for a while the option of monotasking."},{"time":23058,"text":"A couple of examples."},{"time":25973,"text":"Look at that."},{"time":27401,"text":"This is my multitasking activity result. (Laughter)"},{"time":31014,"text":"So trying to cook, answering the phone, writing SMS,"},{"time":34669,"text":"and maybe uploading some pictures"},{"time":37021,"text":"about this awesome barbecue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40539,"text":"So someone tells us the story about supertaskers,"},{"time":44573,"text":"so this two percent of people who are able"},{"time":47998,"text":"to control multitasking environment."},{"time":52134,"text":"But what about ourselves, and what about our reality?"},{"time":56738,"text":"When's the last time you really enjoyed"},{"time":59039,"text":"just the voice of your friend?"},{"time":62309,"text":"So this is a project I'm working on,"},{"time":65565,"text":"and this is a series of front covers"},{"time":70609,"text":"to downgrade our super, hyper â€”"},{"time":75116,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":80033,"text":"to downgrade our super, hyper-mobile phones"},{"time":82841,"text":"into the essence of their function."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85872,"text":"Another example: Have you ever been to Venice?"},{"time":88649,"text":"How beautiful it is to lose ourselves in these little streets"},{"time":92962,"text":"on the island."},{"time":95345,"text":"But our multitasking reality is pretty different,"},{"time":98787,"text":"and full of tons of information."},{"time":103059,"text":"So what about something like that"},{"time":105596,"text":"to rediscover our sense of adventure?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109763,"text":"I know that it could sound pretty weird to speak about mono"},{"time":113036,"text":"when the number of possibilities is so huge,"},{"time":117587,"text":"but I push you to consider the option of"},{"time":122186,"text":"focusing on just one task,"},{"time":125303,"text":"or maybe turning your digital senses totally off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131260,"text":"So nowadays, everyone could produce his mono product."},{"time":137276,"text":"Why not? So find your monotask spot"},{"time":141020,"text":"within the multitasking world."},{"time":143604,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":145137,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}